data.description: WHAT A SWEET FIND, tucked away in the OLA school district!! Charming 4BR/2BATH on a quiet street just waiting for you!! Walk into the FOYER and you will notice the soaring ceilings and open-concept feel. FORMAL DINING ROOM with tall ceilings. GREAT ROOM offers a slate surround gas fireplace and logs. GOURMET KITCHEN has all-new granite counters, recently painted cabinets, a stainless steel gas range, an overhead microwave, and a dishwasher. Subway tile backsplash, stainless steel farmhouse sink, pantry, and eat-at bar. Cozy BREAKFAST ROOM-MASTER SUITE with double tray ceiling. MASTER BATH with new flooring, garden tub, and separate shower. New granite counters with dual sinks, new kitchen height cabinets, new light fixture, and sink/faucet. SPACIOUS GUEST BEDROOMS with new flooring. BONUS OR 4TH BEDROOM upstairs. Outback is perfect for entertaining-extended patio with a covered tin roof, a new pool, decking, and fencing. Many more upgrades, check the disclosure! Keep in mind this is a USDA area as well-100% financing available!
